# 2. Deferred blog: article deep links have no prerendered file, so hydrate the
#    SPA (Contentful loads in the browser). Non-forced 200 -> real files still win.
/blog/*  /index.html  200
/sl/blog/*  /index.html  200

# 3. Anything else that is not a prerendered file is a real 404 (not a Home bounce).
/*  /404.html  404
